            <p class="comment-content">这本基本上就没多少对食物本身的描写与体味，更多的是由食物所发散出的“人文味道”，涉及内容众多，倒是很好的“社会学想象力”范例。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="993325852">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-993325852" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-993325852" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="993325852">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2928579/">烂人贱人在实验室误导大家的昊昊</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-12-30</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">吃饭社会学</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="855221339">
